title: Grateful Dead Live at Sports Arena on 1994-12-18
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Greatest Story Ever Told, Althea, Walkin' Blues,Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, El Paso*, Loose Lucy, Let It Grow

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime-> Crazy Fingers-> Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Space-> The Last Time-> Attics Of My Life;, Johnny B. Goode, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

* Weir on acoustic
